HEADWORD: Propodium
<hw>Pro*po"di*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Propodia</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[NL. See
